trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemStyle"></xref> objects in a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Representa uma coleção de <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemStyle"> </xref> objetos em um <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu"> </xref> controle.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Essa classe não pode ser herdada.

trans-unit.source: The MenuItemStyleCollection class is used to store and manage a collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemStyle> objects in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control.
trans-unit.target: A classe MenuItemStyleCollection é usada para armazenar e gerenciar uma coleção de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemStyle>objetos em um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>controle.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemStyle>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control uses the MenuItemStyleCollection class as the underlying data type of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelMenuItemStyles%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSelectedStyles%2A> properties.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>controle usa a classe de MenuItemStyleCollection como o tipo de dados subjacente a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelMenuItemStyles%2A>e <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSelectedStyles%2A>Propriedades.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSelectedStyles%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelMenuItemStyles%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelMenuItemStyles%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSelectedStyles%2A> properties are an alternative to the individual style properties (such as <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.StaticMenuItemStyle%2A>).
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelMenuItemStyles%2A>e <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSelectedStyles%2A>propriedades são uma alternativa para as propriedades de estilo individuais (como <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.StaticMenuItemStyle%2A>).</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.StaticMenuItemStyle%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSelectedStyles%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelMenuItemStyles%2A>

trans-unit.source: These properties are applied to regular menu items and the selected menu item, respectively, based on the menu item's level in the menu.
trans-unit.target: Essas propriedades são aplicadas aos itens de menu regular e o item de menu selecionado, respectivamente, com base no nível do item de menu no menu.

trans-unit.source: The first style in the collection corresponds to the menu item style for the first level of the menu.
trans-unit.target: O primeiro estilo na coleção corresponde para o estilo do item de menu para o primeiro nível do menu.

trans-unit.source: The second style in the collection corresponds to the menu item style for the second level of the menu, and so on.
trans-unit.target: O segundo estilo na coleção corresponde ao estilo do item de menu para o segundo nível do menu e assim por diante.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelMenuItemStyles%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSelectedStyles%2A> properties are most often used to generate menus where menu items at a certain level have the same appearance, regardless of whether they have submenus.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelMenuItemStyles%2A>e <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSelectedStyles%2A>propriedades são geralmente usadas para gerar menus em que os itens de menu em um determinado nível têm a mesma aparência, independentemente de terem submenus.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSelectedStyles%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelMenuItemStyles%2A>
